{"sections":{"image_with_text_FEypfC":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"enable_section":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Armored-Combat.jpg","layout":"right","title":"Armored Combat Hydration","text":"<p>BioSteel stands out as the premier hydration solution for armored combat participants, addressing the unique challenges faced by fighters in this intense and physically demanding sport. The combination of heavy armor, rigorous physical exertion, and often extreme temperatures creates a perfect storm for rapid dehydration. BioSteel's advanced electrolyte formula is specifically designed to replenish essential minerals lost through profuse sweating, helping combatants maintain optimal hydration levels throughout grueling matches and training sessions. The carefully balanced blend of sodium, potassium, and magnesium supports muscle function and helps prevent cramping, allowing fighters to maintain their strength, agility, and endurance even in the most challenging bouts.<\/p><p>What sets BioSteel apart in the world of armored combat is its clean, natural ingredient profile that aligns with the warrior ethos of many participants. Free from artificial additives and excess sugars, BioSteel provides sustained energy without the crash associated with typical sports drinks. This is crucial for maintaining mental clarity and focus during extended tournaments or training camps. The powder mix format is ideal for fighters, easily transportable and quickly prepared between rounds or matches. Whether facing the intense physical demands of melee combat or the endurance required for longsword duels, BioSteel's superior hydration support helps armored combat athletes perform at their peak, recover faster, and maintain the stamina needed to excel in this unique and challenging sport.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"inf_collection_carousel_KQqfa4":{"type":"INF-CollectionCarousel","settings":{"use_background":false,"background":"#ffffff","heading":"Armored Combat